flowRoot.flowPara: YEGRB's mission is to grow the Ruby community in Edmonton, Canada. Come out to our next meetup, or write some code together at our next hackup!

Fork this site on GitHub to submit changes!
Come out to our next meetup and help us celebrate our first year in Edmonton. To honour our one-year anniversary we're partnering with StartupEdmonton to create the first ever BuildNight in Edmonton!

We'll be building a Twitter clone in 2 hours using Ruby and Rails in front of a live audience at the UofA! Expect a behind-the-scenes look at how real developers work and improve their productivity with Ruby.
